# Agent Execution Rule

Agents must follow strict boundaries.

NEVER:
- Modify unrelated files
- Mix UI + engine + data changes in one task
- Refactor large parts of the system without request
- Commit automatically

ALWAYS:
- Work in the specified files only
- Respect task scope
- Prefer small, safe changes
- Stop if unexpected issues appear

If task scope is unclear:
- Ask before proceeding